org.daisy.common.spi

Interface CreateOnStart


  • public interface CreateOnStart
    Tag interface for indicating that a component is to be created immediately when the program starts. This can be accomplished by making the component available through META-INF/services and executing the following code in the program's main method: 
     
 for (CreateOnStart c : ServiceLoader.load(CreateOnStart.class));
